main_body:
Decision 2010/670/EU is amended as follows:
(1) Article 9 is amended as follows:
(a) in the first paragraph, ‘24 months’ is replaced by ‘48 months’;
(b) in the second paragraph, ‘36 months’ is replaced by ‘60 months’;
(2) Article 11(1) is amended as follows:
(a) in the second subparagraph ‘31 December 2015’ is replaced by ‘31 December 2017’ and ‘4 years’ is replaced by ‘6 years’;
(b) the following third and fourth subparagraphs are added:
